# Wisp's Vigil (Phaser 3 + Vite + TypeScript)

## Stack
- Phaser 3.88+, Vite 6, strict TypeScript
- World size: 800×600 (`src/game/state.ts`)

## Boundaries
- **Game rules & spawners:** `src/game/**` only
- **Damage pipeline:** `src/game/PlayerDamage.ts`
- **Phaser scenes:** `src/scenes/**` — orchestration only
- **HUD & juice:** `src/ui/**` — reads `GameState`; no spawn/score rules
- **Assets:** `src/assets/**`; binaries in `public/assets/`

## State (`GameState`)
- `health`, `maxHealth`, `armor`, `maxArmor` (no legacy `shields`)
- Single source: `src/game/state.ts`
- Registry key: `gameState`

## Spritesheet
- `entities.png` 4×6 grid; run `npm run pack:sprites` after PNG changes
- Pickup types: soul, vitality, plating — archer row 5
- Boss/projectile/obstacle: separate PNGs

## Commands
- `npm run dev` / `npm run build` / `npm run pack:sprites`
